exercises.name: HAMSTRING STRETCH -ACTIVE MUSCLE ENGAGEMENT
exercises.reminders: The simple stretching exercises target tightness in your hamstring and calf muscles. If you are also tight in IT Band, stretch that as well. Progression: stretching begins with the hamstrings then moves to calves and IT Band.
